  "description": "A single kick voice in full Atmosphere mode — long decay, maximum body, deep reverb tail. No hat, no snare, no supporting structure. The kick is the whole event. Its sub energy fills the entire space. PUNCH macro controls transient sharpness; SPACE macro extends the reverb room size. Monolithic and isolating.",
